summary: Country music star Morgan Wallen has been arrested and charged with felony reckless endangerment after being accused of throwing a chair from the rooftop of a Nashville bar. The incident occurred at the Chief's bar, owned by fellow country singer Eric Church, where Wallen was reportedly seen on surveillance video throwing the chair off the roof. Witnesses stated that the chair could have hit pedestrians below, causing serious injury or death. Wallen was subsequently arrested and released on bond. His ex-girlfriend, KT Smith, responded to the news of his arrest, expressing concern and sadness.

name: Can you take a picture of the eclipse
summary: With the highly anticipated solar eclipse approaching, it is crucial to understand how to safely capture this celestial event using your phone. While phones allow for eclipse photography, caution is advised. Experts warn against directly pointing your phone's camera at the sun due to potential damage to the lens or camera sensor. However, indirect methods exist to capture the eclipse safely, such as using a solar filter or holding a piece of eclipse glasses over the camera. Additionally, adjusting camera settings and using specific apps can enhance the quality of your eclipse photos.

name: Jonathan Majors
summary: Actor Jonathan Majors has been sentenced to probation and domestic violence counseling following his conviction for assaulting his ex-girlfriend. The incident occurred in 2020 and resulted in Majors pleading no contest to felony domestic violence charges. As part of his sentence, Majors will be required to attend a year-long anti-domestic violence program and undergo mental health treatment. The judge's decision to avoid jail time has been met with mixed reactions, with some critics arguing that it sends the wrong message about domestic violence.

name: J. Cole
summary: J. Cole has retracted his diss track against Kendrick Lamar, titled "7 Minute Drill". The song, which was released as part of Cole's surprise album "Might Delete Later," featured Cole taking aim at Lamar's recent music and his alleged infidelity. Cole's apology comes just two days after the track's release, with the rapper expressing regret over the diss and stating that he had already regretted the lyrics. The track was met with mixed reactions, with some praising Cole's lyricism while others criticized him for attacking Lamar. The incident highlights the ongoing feud between Cole and Lamar, which stems fromLamar's perceived slight of Cole on his 2015 track "King Kunta."

name: Purdue University
summary: Purdue University has been featured prominently in recent news headlines. SK hynix has announced a significant investment in semiconductor advanced packaging at Purdue Research Park, fostering a partnership between the university and the company. Purdue and SK hynix further collaborated on a $3.87 billion investment in semiconductors. Purdue University has also garnered attention for its upcoming Final Four basketball game against NC State, prompting inquiries about its location. Additionally, Purdue University Northwest students commemorated International Math Day, and a UTSA VP received an award for their engineering achievements from Purdue University. Purdue University administrators have recently announced merit increases for faculty and staff at Purdue University Northwest and a salary policy for 2024-25 for Purdue faculty and staff. The university also hosted an event to observe the solar eclipse, drawing a large crowd.

name: Solar eclipse 2024 Michigan
summary: In 2024, a total solar eclipse will traverse Michigan, generating significant interest. Luna Pier, the only location in the state along the path of totality, is expected to experience heavy traffic and early crowds. Observers can anticipate "eerie" shadows and quiet wildlife during the eclipse's full coverage. Several resources provide comprehensive guides to the event, including specific viewing times and locations throughout Michigan, with the eclipse's peak occurring on April 8th. These sources emphasize the importance of planning ahead to avoid traffic congestion and capture the optimal viewing experience.
